item.title: Aspose.Drawing for Java 23.12 Release Notes
item.description: This page contains release notes information for Aspose.Drawing for Java 23.12. Improvements and Changes The initial release of Aspose.Drawing for Java - cross-platform graphic library implementing easy-to-use comprehensive drawing API, including image manipulation, vector and text drawing in fully managed code without any external dependencies.
